div.stage:
(Music. - March - The Emperor Napoleon distributes papers among the
officers in front, the infantry and cavalry are fully occupied at the back,
while the officers fill out the front.)

sp.p:
 Thou should’st well remember then the cruelties inflicted upon defenceless
inhabitants - our husbands, children, in cold blood murdered. Now, answer me;
hast thou a wife and children?
